<node id="Large Language Models (LLMs)">
  <data key="d0">Large Language Models (LLMs)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Models that are enhanced by Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) Systems to generate more accurate and contextually relevant responses.&lt;SEP&gt;Large Language Models (LLMs) are utilized by LightRAG for text analysis, processing, and the identification and extraction of various entities and relationships.&lt;SEP&gt;Large Language Models (LLMs) are a focus of various research papers, often augmented with retrieval capabilities.&lt;SEP&gt;Models utilized in the LightRAG framework for various operations, including entity and relationship extraction and the retrieve-and-generate process.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-69aa0eae6d1f6ab69e22f063ae2a2e46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0747de8554c174a10ea77615f403b7d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4549fd8b07fec5e027d7fa32b14bf264&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c80e23a4f1cc3df3c051d5673ddddb5</data>
