  <data key="d0">Heart Disease</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Heart Disease is a potential medical issue that cardiologists assess symptoms to identify, used as an example entity for extraction.&lt;SEP&gt;An example entity representing a medical condition that cardiologists diagnose.</data>
