<node id="Knowledge Base">
  <data key="d0">Knowledge Base</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The accumulated information that LightRAG incrementally updates to adapt to evolving data changes, ensuring accurate and relevant responses.&lt;SEP&gt;The knowledge base is the collection of documents or information used by the system, which can be expanded.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47f20c669a70fff5620e01924436985d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bb0821a8bce14dc43249aa4d2557124</data>
