<node id="LightRAG Framework">
  <data key="d0">LightRAG Framework</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The LightRAG Framework is a proposed system for retrieval-augmented answer generation, incorporating high-order relatedness and dual-level retrieval.&lt;SEP&gt;A framework whose methodologies and experimental settings are elaborated, detailing steps for entity and relationship extraction using LLMs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-406bf69e556a29330cb91c63e689dffc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c80e23a4f1cc3df3c051d5673ddddb5</data>
