  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The Graph-based Retrieval Phase is the second part of the LightRAG framework, utilizing an LLM to generate relevant keywords for vector-based search.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-406bf69e556a29330cb91c63e689dffc</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1768751033</data>
