  <data key="d0">ngrok</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">ngrok is a service and tool that exposes local servers to the internet via secure tunnels.&lt;SEP&gt;A tool used to create a secure tunnel and expose a local server to the internet.&lt;SEP&gt;A tool used to expose a local API server to the internet via an HTTPS tunnel.&lt;SEP&gt;A service used to create secure tunnels to local development servers, making them accessible over the internet.</data>
